---
import Icon from '@/components/icons/Icons.astro'
---

<section class="py-[var(--space-section)]">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="glass-panel w-full p-8 md:p-16 lg:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden reveal" data-reveal>
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-[var(--color-brand)]/[0.04] rounded-full blur-3xl translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <p class="section-label text-[var(--color-brand)] mb-6">Contact</p>
        <h2 class="page-title mb-6 text-center">相談は、まだ輪郭が<br />曖昧な段階でも大丈夫です。</h2>
        <p class="body-text max-w-xl text-center mb-10">
          フロントエンドの技術選定、アーキテクチャ設計、または現在抱えているプロダクトの運用課題について、ざっくばらんにお話ししましょう。
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="group btn-primary">
          Start a conversation
          <Icon name="arrow-right" size={14} class="hover-arrow" />
        </a>
        <p class="caption mt-4">AI integration / Automation / Product build</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
